strong>五毛分化就係要我哋失去互信！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"491575764ba18c1cf6c8c0082c51b3bc3b0af794","tid":1299628,"uid":128763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:45:45.000Z","msg":"如果要會面要有策略先得<br />\n始終你對住嘅係一個老奸巨滑嘅人"},{"pid":"909f00d568cb00fa1b84daeea8ef1fbda70390af","tid":1299628,"uid":128763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"唔應該妥協任何野"},{"pid":"1f1fa7c134aa859678cc83a757f2690e5e512f12","tid":1299628,"uid":240785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:54:37.000Z","msg":"其實 會面 或 拒絕會面 都要有策略， 唔可以被分化。<br />\n如果會面一定要做足準備，唔好俾佢帶住，要由學生做主導，講想講嘅話題（5 大訴求），同埋要佢解釋點解唔做，（記住係用理據， 如習近平都有特赦等等）<br />\n如果拒絕會面，亦要準備一下政府會講到政府想傾，只係學生唔肯見，指控學生一意孤行，根本無心解決問題。"},{"pid":"b0162ba87e3b89b1f0cc9ff88fb93811b4b8f0c2","tid":1299628,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:59:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"89d068304fe90a63f0d689abe06b77192ffdd69a","tid":1299628,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:23:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"809b90cfa1b90299cb6f9c81a2c75f2ac13c486b","tid":1299628,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7feff32868f9ac749b2a8718809ca02f1ec5d43","tid":1299628,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"822c31423658093f8a7e5d9b6d7402e039557db3","tid":1299628,"uid":142574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52d9f321481b05de118d572df68081b0d931b080","tid":1299628,"uid":153258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:13:52.000Z","msg":"大家以史為鑑 林鄭係冇退縮過 唔好中計"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:18:44.000Z","msg":"當年8964都係會面後屠城，而家政府連小小讓步都無，根本無野好傾！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:26:44.000Z","msg":"用返香港歷史<br />\n雨革一樣係傾條毛之後清場"},{"pid":"70070f131e8a54e7d383d003275a9148567c274d","tid":1299628,"uid":272196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:29:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e8f541bd4d0ca648ca555948e70a6c8b4fa8070d","tid":1299628,"uid":232766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bb5699c05297aec88e910f7a3cc4e8d325ff3fe9","tid":1299628,"uid":276002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6238a7006727befbb7472a4049852988c0cb633d","tid":1299628,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:49:36.000Z","msg":"可以會面，訊求加埋取消確認書同埋雙普選"},{"pid":"16aec73a03e50f51a378f7f3e24a27719e97acb9","tid":1299628,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實你明唔明 見面係一張好重要的雙面劍<br />\n一見面等同運動落幕 係最後先做的野來 玩到最後大家都唔玩而出來的Deal<br />\n<br />\n如果一見等同認同政府釋出善意 中間人士會立即轉向 無論最後傾唔傾得埋<br />\n而且會面失敗佐 對依邊都同樣有打擊士氣的作用"}]}